## Phase 5.5 — Choice → Action Binding + Narrative Feedback

**Date:** 2026-04-04 21:15  
**Status:** ✅ Complete  
**Tests:** 33 passed (Phase 5) + 43 passed (Phase 4)

---

### Overview

This phase adds the missing glue layer between narrative choices and simulation actions:

```
Before: Narrative → Choices (cosmetic only)
After:  Narrative → Choices → Actions → Simulation → New Narrative
```

